{
  "stem": "25809.5",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I went to Australia, 19 years old, no profession really.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I-- I arrived with $50 in my pocket.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I had a room.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Nobody came to pick me up from the-- from-- when I arrived because there was nobody there.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Except I had a telegram from a cousin of mine who was too far away to pick me up and said, I got a room for you there [INAUDIBLE], which was at the [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I-- I had some names of people that maybe that might help me.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I had no job.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I got there, and within one week, I managed to get a job in a-- a distributor-- winery, beer wholesaler in downtown Sydney.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I won't give you the-- the trip of the which was a migrant ship and was a terrible place.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It was terrible, smelly.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I remember one of the engineers saying, [NON-ENGLISH SPEECH] like the devil was on the ship because everything broke down.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, we were for four days in the Indian Ocean stuck with a broken-down engine.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Anyhow, they repaired it, and we got to Sydney after about 30, 33 days at sea.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Anyhow, I started working there, and I lost the job.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Actually, the first year that I was in Sydney I had 13 jobs.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I remember distinctly because I had to fill in my tax papers, and there was not enough room to put all the jobs that I had been in.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Couldn't find anything that worked for me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And finally, I got-- I got a job as a waiter.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And I-- I had never been a waiter, and I didn't know a darn thing about being a waiter.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "But my cousin, meanwhile, had told me that-- what to do as a waiter.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
